{
  "stem": "142.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1933, was quite a bit of anti-Semitism, especially in the Jewish neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were two, three neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, at that time, was the-- they call it the Three Es were an organization that was against-- against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three Epsilon they call it in Greek was an organization that was against the Jews at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they would try to burn the neighborhoods or do-- you know, put fires.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that's why my uncle that lived in a different neighborhood, you know, decide to take his family and go-- at that time, go into Palestine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1933.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were all aware what was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I-- I think since we were Italian citizens, they wouldn't-- they were-- they knew where we were, so we were pretty safe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had all kinds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, first of all, we had a lot of Italian-- Italian books and newspapers, and especially Greek newspapers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was working, bringing home all the time the newspaper he was working on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, always.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I always-- I like-- I don't read books enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I read a lot of magazines and newspapers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always want-- want to find out what the world is all about.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were reading-- no, especially in 1939 when the war started, you know, with Germany, you know, declaring war to Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, you know, then the Italians also, in-- a year later in 1940, declared war to Greece.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what happened, during that time, that the Greeks took our family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They left my father and my little brother home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And me, my brother, and my father, they took us in a camp, a concentration camp in southern Greece.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Argos, Greece.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that was the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
